00:18:58.690 --> 00:19:05.690
We get a glimpse of Roman life back then, with this multi-story apartment buildings known as Insule,

00:19:05.690 --> 00:19:10.690
along with temples, theatres, thermal baths, and shops.

00:19:10.690 --> 00:19:15.690
Walking through the old streets, it's easy to imagine our brothers witnessing to the people.

00:19:15.690 --> 00:19:30.690
Perhaps they stopped to eat at a food shop similar to this one, called Thermopolyur, where you could buy bread, wine, roasted meat, cheese, and have some refreshment.

00:19:30.690 --> 00:19:36.690
