00:20:04.690 --> 00:20:11.690
The criminals were also put to death here. Interestingly, entry to the Colosseum was free.

00:20:11.690 --> 00:20:18.690
This was part of the policy of the Amperors, who offered free entertainment in order to keep the people under control.

00:20:18.690 --> 00:20:24.690
